      • toString

        public String toString(boolean toPortion)
        Parameters:
        toPortion - allowed object is Boolean
        Returns:
        the classification of a classified set of data, either full or portion based on the boolean parameter. If True, the String returned applies to a section, part, paragraph, or similar portion. If False, the String returned is the full classification and associated markings.
